The NEWS file for RDFetch.
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
v0.4.13 -- 29 October 2021

Changes:
   Refactor rdfetch to use xmlstarlet(1) instead of xsltproc(1)
   Significant whitespace cleanup
   Move function getYesNo() to zsh-functions
   Other minor cleanup and clarifications
   
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
v0.4.12 -- 27 September 2021

Changes:
   Fix typo in sendNotification() in zsh-functions
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
v0.4.11 -- 27 September 2021

Changes:
   shellcheck corrections in rdfetch
   Fix the use of ${HOSTNAME} in zsh-functions
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
v0.4.3 -- 18 April 2021

Changes:
   Many fixes and improvements.
   Support Rivendell 3.x dropbox reset and restart.
   Add simple Event creation after successful dropbox creation.
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
v0.3.7 -- 30 March 2021

Changes:
   Updates to zsh-functions (shellcheck, etc.)
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
v0.3.6 -- 19 August 2020

Initial release.
